43
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:20,619
- She's the daughter of the traitor Li Jiancheng.
- Take hold of Wang Junkuo!

44
00:03:20,619 --> 00:03:22,919
- Yes.
- Shen Gu! You...

45
00:03:22,919 --> 00:03:26,779
The Prince of Lujiang rose in rebellion, now take all the people in his house for trial.

46
00:03:26,779 --> 00:03:28,240
Shen Gu!

47
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:31,080
I offered advice for your own sake. I didn't expect you to not be able to tell good from the bad.
<i>[Governor Manor]</i>

48
00:03:31,080 --> 00:03:32,160
