According to the command as the Aide of the Crown Prince, I'm here to capture the betrayers.

72
00:04:59,618 --> 00:05:02,320
I'm the general of the city wall of You State, Shen Gu.

73
00:05:02,320 --> 00:05:03,939
Envoy Wei has already reported.

74
00:05:03,939 --> 00:05:05,619
